08Chan
It is convenient that once you view a file, you don't need to download it when accessing it again. However posting images from tor seems partially of broken: only the thumbnail seems to works. When posting CYOAs tor should be disabled unless this is fixed.

~~Edit: The issue I ran into might or might not be due to tor. Spoke then realized I hadn't confirmed it enough to speak like I knew what I was talking about.~~
Disabling fingerprinting only fixes the thumbnail in 08chan. Uploading images using tor works on Millchan with fingerprinting on or off. An update should fix the issue completely.

Yes. It might be broken for you because of the recent update. If 08chan is missing lots of stuff try rebuilding and reloading from the zero menu (drag the icon to the left to access the menu), then restart.

>Download All
Should download all files in a post, but it doesn't work for me. Making sure all files in the post are seeded and/or using Chrome might work.
>Seed All
Seed all files in a post.
>Help Seed Files
Seed the files that user posts. Haven't used it, don't know exactly how it works.
>Pin Board
Pin seeded files on that board so they won't get deleted when you run low on space. I think it only pins files you're already seeding.
